 Netflix在创纪录的用户增加后提高英国订阅费https://www.nme.com/news/tv/netflix-raises-uk-subscription-following-following-record-user-increase-3836146?utm_source=rscce = rss＆utm_medium = rsss＆utm_campaign = netflix-subscription-compription-ukscription-netflix-raiss-raiss-raiss-raiss-raises-raises-raises-raises-raises-fees-fees-fees-fees-fees以下记录 - 用户加入Chris EdwardsFri, 07 Feb 2025 19:50:20 +0000 Film NewsNewsTV NewsNetflix https://www.nme.com/?p=3836146 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/netflix-the-influencer-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Netflix影响者" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/netflix-the-influencer-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/netflix-the-influencer-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/netflix-the-influencer-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/netflix-the-influencer-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/netflix-the-influencer-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/netflix-the-influencer-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>没有广告的标准订阅现在每月的价格为12.99英镑</p><p>Netflix帖子在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首先出现<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/netflix-raises-uk-subscription-fees-following-record-user-increase-3836146">在创纪录的用户增加之后的英国订阅费用</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/netflix-the-influencer-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Netflix影响者" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/netflix-the-influencer-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/netflix-the-influencer-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/netflix-the-influencer-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/netflix-the-influencer-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/netflix-the-influencer-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/netflix-the-influencer-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a>上个月在美国，加拿大，阿根廷和葡萄牙提高了费用后，在英国提高了订阅价格。</p><p>对于英国客户而言，没有广告的标准订阅价格每月上涨2至12.99英镑，其他包裹也在增加。</p><p>最便宜的选择 - 带广告的标准订阅 - 每月上涨1英镑至5.99英镑，而最昂贵的高级订阅也增加了1英镑至18.99英镑。</p><p>该平台还将其额外成员附加组件的费用增加1英镑，这意味着现在将额外的用户添加到带有广告的标准订阅中，而将额外的用户添加为4.99英镑，而在没有的情况下将额外的用户添加到没有的情况下广告。</p><p>现在，价格变化反映在Netflix的网站上，新费用适用于新客户和现有客户。</p><p> Netflix发言人在一份<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/c98yrp0pyrjo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">声明</a>中说，价格上涨将使流媒体“继续投资于我们的成员的编程和交付价值”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3832636" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3832636" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3832636" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Squid-Game-season-two3.jpg" alt="玩家456 Gi-Hun（Lee Jung-jae）在“鱿鱼游戏”第二季中。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Squid-Game-season-two3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Squid-Game-season-two3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Squid-Game-season-two3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Squid-Game-season-two3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Squid-Game-season-two3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Squid-Game-season-two3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3832636" class="wp-caption-text">玩家456 Gi-Hun（Lee Jung-jae）在“鱿鱼游戏”第二季中。学分：Netflix</figcaption></figure><p>该流媒体服务报道了2024年底的全球订户数字，部分原因是韩国戏剧系列Squid游戏的第二季以及它不断扩大的体育报道。</p><p>该公司表示，它完成了2024年，总共超过3亿。在去年的10月和12月之间，预计将增加960万新用户，但远远超过了这个数字，在一年的最后一个月中增加了1900万订户。</p><p>该平台在圣诞节那天播放了两场NFL比赛，并举办了有影响力的战斗机杰克·保罗（Jake Paul）和前世界重量级冠军迈克·泰森（Mike Tyson）之间的拳击比赛，两者都吸引了创纪录的收视率。</p><p> Netflix并不是近几个月来提高其订阅费用的唯一平台。<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/disney">迪士尼+</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/spotify">Spotify</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/paramount">Paramount+</a>等主要彩带在2024年在全球范围内也提高了价格。</p><p> 2023年5月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/netflix-password-sharing-restrictions-explained-3391288#:~:text=Netflix%20has%20announced%20the%20details,new%20system%20on%20their%20website.">Netflix开始在英国和美国执行密码共享禁令</a>，这导致了次年数百万新的注册。</p><p> Netflix帖子在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首先出现<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/netflix-raises-uk-subscription-fees-following-record-user-increase-3836146">在创纪录的用户增加之后的英国订阅费用</a>。</p> ;
